OL,3,CStudy pinpoints 'critical time
OL,4,Cwindows' for illnesses that pose
OL,5,Cdementia risk
OL,7,FDeveloping illnesses such as heart
OL,8,Fdisease and diabetes before the age of
OL,9,F55 could increase the chance of having
OL,10,Fdementia in later life, a new study
OL,11,Fsuggests.
OL,13,FStrokes or the onset of mental health
OL,14,Fconditions such as anxiety and
OL,15,Fdepression between 55 and 70 could
OL,16,Falso increase risk two-fold, according
OL,17,Fto research.
