OL,3,CStudy pinpoints 'critical time
OL,4,Cwindows' for illnesses that pose
OL,5,Cdementia risk
OL,7,FExperts at the University of Oxford
OL,8,Fsaid up to 80% of dementia patients
OL,9,Fsuffer from two or more chronic health
OL,10,Fconditions, but there is a "lack of
OL,11,Funderstanding" when it comes to
OL,12,Fspecific illnesses, age of onset and
OL,13,Fthe link to dementia.
OL,15,FThey identified "critical time
OL,16,Fwindows" in which certain illnesses
OL,17,Fpose the greatest risk to patients.
