OL,3,CStudy pinpoints 'critical time
OL,4,Cwindows' for illnesses that pose
OL,5,Cdementia risk
OL,7,FFor the study, published in Brain
OL,8,FCommunications, researchers analysed
OL,9,Fdata from 282,712 people using the UK
OL,10,FBiobank and looked at patterns for 46
OL,11,Fchronic health conditions.
OL,13,FThey found that heart conditions such
OL,14,Fas heart disease and atrial
OL,15,Ffibrillation, as well as diabetes,
OL,16,Fbefore the age of 55 was most strongly
OL,17,Flinked to dementia risk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
