OL,3,CStudy pinpoints 'critical time
OL,4,Cwindows' for illnesses that pose
OL,5,Cdementia risk
OL,7,FMs Suri said the presence of other
OL,8,Fillnesses should be taken into account
OL,9,Fwhen estimating a person's risk of
OL,10,Fdeveloping dementia, and could help
OL,11,Fdevelop strategies that aim to reduce
OL,12,Frisk at certain points in life.
OL,14,FShe added: "This study identified
OL,15,Fassociations between multimorbidity
OL,16,Fand dementia risk but we need to
OL,17,Funderstand more about why this happens.
