OL,3,CStudy pinpoints 'critical time
OL,4,Cwindows' for illnesses that pose
OL,5,Cdementia risk
OL,7,F"We also need to try to replicate the
OL,8,Fstudy in more diverse groups of people
OL,9,Fto ensure the results are
OL,10,Frepresentative of the population.
OL,12,F"Future studies could examine whether
OL,13,Fefforts to manage or prevent
OL,14,Fcardiovascular problems in early-to-
OL,15,Fmidlife, followed by mental health and
OL,16,Fneurological disorders when people are
OL,17,Fin their fifties and sixties, might
OL,18,Freduce the risk of dementia."
